0.10.1
---
Feature
- RibbonBar: use sizeHint to limit the minimum width of mainwindow

Optimize
- RibbonStyleOption: the other height of group includes margin and title
- WindowButtonGroup: reserve 1px bottom margin to prevent covering tabBarBaseLine
- RibbonTabBar: set the style of navigation buttons
- DarkOfficePlus: use stronger background for selected
- RibbonBar: paint page context within the visible area
- qss: set background for MenuButtonPopup button
- ubuntu: qss: set the background of menu-button to transparent

Bugfix
- RibbonWindow: fix the shown when setting frameless
- RibbonButton: ubuntu: fix the position of menu arrow
- RibbonButton: fix the drawing of Qt::ToolButtonTextOnly style
- ubuntu: qss: fix the white bg of QComboBox item in dark theme

0.10.0
---
Feature
- Support RibbonTabBar unselect all tabs
- Add OfficePlus Dark theme
- Add native RibbonMainWindow

Interface
- RibbonWindow: inherit RibbonMainWindow instead of QMainWindow
- WindowButtonGroup: remove setButtonWidthStretch,setWindowBorder
- RibbonGroup: add title,setTitle compatible with other ribbon framework
- RibbonPage: add title,setTitle,groups compatible with other ribbon framework

Optimize
- RibbonQuickAccessBar: perfect control action visible
- WindowButtonGroup: manually send leave event to maximizeButton
- RibbonTabBar: only handle the valid click area
- RibbonTabBar: use tabSizeHint to control tab height
- WindowButton: use SizePolicy to control height
- WindowButton: inherit QToolButton instead of QPushButton


0.9.1
---
Interface
- RibbonBar: add clearPages
- RibbonPage: add clearGroups
- RibbonGroup: using QWidget::addAction

Optimize
- qss: adjust tab text alignment
- RibbonGridContainer: handle enter event to deactive menu action

Bugfix
- native: win: fix build failure on qt5.12.12

0.9.0
---
Feature
- Add RibbonGridContainer class as widget of RibbonMenu
- Support for setting TabBar position in RibbonBar

Interface
- RibbonButton: remove setLiteStyleEnableWordWrap,isLiteStyleEnableWordWrap
- RibbonBar: remove rightButtonGroup,activeRightButtonGroup
- RibbonBar: remove tabBarBaseLineColor,setTabBarBaseLineColor
- RibbonBar: remove ribbonTabBar
- RibbonGallery: remove getPopupViewPort
- RibbonPageContext: remove id,setId
- RibbonMenu: split from ribboncontrols file, make it independent
- Privatize RibbonGalleryViewport,RibbonTabBar
- Perfect customize widgets
- qss: rename prefix and ThemeStyles

Optimize
- Optimize RibbonStyleOption


